System utilization for 2025-11-26 can be determined by analyzing the resource usage metrics, including CPU time, I/O counts, and data transfer volumes, across different workload types and applications.

  • The data provides resource usage metrics aggregated by date, hour, day of the week, workload type, workload complexity, username, and application ID.

  • Applications EDITOR and PYTHON3.13 are responsible for most of the resource utilization.
